## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="211bc-102">인스턴스 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs> 때 작성 되는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> 발생 시키는 개체는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.EmulateRecognizeCompleted> 이벤트입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="211bc-102">An instance of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs> is created when the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> object raises the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.EmulateRecognizeCompleted> event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="211bc-103">인식의 결과 대 한 정보를 얻으려면 액세스는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> 이벤트에 대 한 처리기에서 속성입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="211bc-103">To obtain information about the result of recognition, access the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> property in the handler for the event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="211bc-104">에뮬레이션 하는 프로세스는 기준인 오디오 대신 텍스트 음성 인식 엔진에 대 한 입력은입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="211bc-104">Emulation is the process by which text, instead of audio, is the input to a speech recognition engine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="211bc-105">에 대 한 오디오 입력을 무시 하는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> 에뮬레이션을 사용 하는 동안 개체는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SetInputToNull%2A> 메서드.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="211bc-105">To bypass the audio inputs for a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> object during emulation, use the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SetInputToNull%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="211bc-106">음성 인식 엔진에서 인식 작업 중에 예외가 발생 하는 경우는 <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A> 예외 속성 및 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> 속성이 `null`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="211bc-106">If the speech recognition engine encounters an exception during the recognition operation, the <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A> property is set to the exception and the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> property is set to `null`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="211bc-107"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs>은 <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs>로부터 파생됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="211bc-107"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs> derives from <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="211bc-108">에 대 한 이벤트 처리기를 추가 하는 다음 예제는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.EmulateRecognizeCompleted> 이벤트를 한 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="211bc-108">The following example adds an event handler for the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.EmulateRecognizeCompleted> event to a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="211bc-109">처리기가에서 인식된 된 텍스트는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> 속성입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="211bc-109">The handler gets the recognized text from the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
  
private SpeechRecognitionEngine sre;  
  
// Initialize the speech recognition engine.   
private void Initialize()  
{  
  sre = new SpeechRecognitionEngine();  
  
  // Add a handler for the EmulateRecognizeCompleted event.  
  sre.EmulateRecognizeCompleted += new EventHandler<EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs>(sre_EmulateRecognizeCompleted);  
  
  // Add other initialization code here.  
}  
  
// Handle the EmulateRecognizeCompleted event.   
void sre_EmulateRecognizeCompleted(object sender, EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs e)  
{  
  if (e.Result == null) return;  
  
  string phrase = e.Result.Text;  
  
  // Add event handler code here.  
}  
  
```
